			<technologicalApplicability xml:lang="en">Lithium hexafluorophosphate produced by the fluorine-free gas method is commonly used as an electrolyte in lithium-ion batteries, which power electronic devices such as smartphones, laptops, and electric vehicles. This high-purity compound is crucial for battery performance and longevity.</technologicalApplicability>
			<technologicalApplicability xml:lang="zh">采用无氟气法生产的六氟磷酸锂通常用作锂离子电池的电解质，这些电池为智能手机、笔记本电脑和电动汽车等电子设备供电。这种高纯度化合物对电池性能和寿命至关重要。</technologicalApplicability>
