			<useAdviceForDataSet xml:lang="en">When utilizing this data for Life Cycle Assessment of products containing lithium hexafluorophosphate, consider the source and purity level of the material. Ensure to account for any environmental impacts associated with the production phase, which utilizes a fluorine-free gas method. This may affect the overall environmental footprint in comparison to other production processes. Also, consider future recycling possibilities and end-of-life scenarios for products containing this substance.</useAdviceForDataSet>
			<useAdviceForDataSet xml:lang="zh">在使用这些数据进行含有六氟磷酸锂产品的生命周期评估时，需考虑材料的来源和纯度。确保考虑采用无氟气法的生产阶段相关的环境影响。这可能会影响与其他生产工艺相比的整体环境足迹。同时，也应考虑包含此物质的产品的未来回收可能性和生命周期终端场景。</useAdviceForDataSet>
